            <h3>Pingtree (https://pingtree.com) </h3>

        <p>    
            We are a SaaS company who's developed an angular based web application geared towards providing users with full funnel marketing and analytics platform. Our small team has taken a vision and turned 
            it into an incredibly complex and dynamic platform that's highly capable. While there are other applications and platforms in the lead generation and marketing analytics space,
            there aren't any that allow users the functionality all-in-one. 

            Throughout the last year, we have developed and implemented several modules including: 

                <list>

                    1. Campaign Management
                    2. Media Buying
                    3. Creatives Library
                    4. Treehouse: A unique marketplace which allows users to faciliate the buying and/or selling of lead traffic in any business vertical
                    5. Real-Time Payments and User Wallet Integration
                    6. Webflows
                    7. Route 53 DNS Services for easy domain integration and connections

                </list>
                
            
